(540, 'MEIS-UA 518', 51, 2, 'Topics in Middle Eastern History: Critical Approac', 'Critical Approaches to Modernism and Modernity Nationalism and Sectarian Identity in the Middle E Advanced undergraduate course that focuses on specic issues in Middle Eastern history. Topics vary each time it is offered.', 4, '', 1, 0),
