(3985, 'MPASS-GE 2161', 443, 17, 'Violin Pedagogy', 'An examination of graded technical material, repertoire & teaching methods. Studies will include how to teach various technical concepts, working with various fingerings & bowings & the correct progression of repertoire. The emphasis will be on understanding how students learn mentally & physically.', 0, '', 1, 0),
